OL,3,CRising cost of oil due to Middle East
OL,4,Cconflict prompts warning over fuel
OL,5,Cthefts
OL,7,FThe rising cost of oil in the UK,
OL,8,Flinked to the ongoing Middle East
OL,9,Fconflict - has prompted a warning from
OL,10,FHampshire Police over possible fuel
OL,11,Fthefts.
OL,13,FThe Force says criminals will take the
OL,14,Fopportunity to profit from the cost
OL,15,Fincreases.
OL,17,FDiesel theft is a problem for many
OL,18,Ffarms and rural properties, with fuel
OL,19,Ftanks stored in rural and isolated
OL,20,Flocations proving attractive to
OL,21,Fthieves looking for an easy target.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
