OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774177608
OL,3,CRising cost of oil due to Middle East
OL,4,Cconflict prompts warning over fuel
OL,5,Cthefts
OL,7,FIt's urging those who use domestic oil
OL,8,Fto keep fuel tanks visible from the
OL,9,Fhouse - and install cameras and alarms.
OL,11,FPolice say as many people rely on
OL,12,Fheating oil to keep their homes warm,
OL,13,Fcriminals will watch the market and
OL,14,Ftake the opportunity to profit from
OL,15,Fcost increases.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
