OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774177608
OL,3,CRising cost of oil due to Middle East
OL,4,Cconflict prompts warning over fuel
OL,5,Cthefts
OL,7,FOfficers are urging people to ensure
OL,8,Ffuel tanks are visible from the house
OL,9,Fto increase the chance of a thief
OL,10,Fbeing seen, use motion-sensor security
OL,11,Flighting and consider installing a
OL,12,Fmotion-sensor alarm in this area.
OL,14,FDiesel theft is also a problem for
OL,15,Fmany farms and rural properties, so
OL,16,Fpeople are warned to keep tanks stored
OL,17,Fclose to the property where you can
OL,18,Fsee them.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
